        <h2>Direwolf20 FTB Pack</h2>
        <p>Athens currently hosts a Direwolf20 modded Minecraft server. To play, after you've been whitelisted, you will need to download the Feed the Beast launcher at this link:
        </p>
      <p><%= link_to 'Feed The Beast', 'http://www.feed-the-beast.com' %></p>

      <p>Once you've downloaded it, and run the launcher, you will select the Direwolf20 pack from the list on the left. You will also need to change the version dropdown from 'Recommended' to '1.0.21' - this is located directly under the 'maps' tab. Once that's done, click "Launch" and the pack will download and install for you. If the server version changes, it will always be visible when you attempt to connect to the server in the server description. We try to update this about once a week.
      </p>
