        <h4><Strong>Server Addreses</strong></h4>
         <p><strong>Minecraft IP:</strong> dire.athensmc.com</p>
         <p><strong>Mumble IP:</strong> mumble.athensmc.com (port: 64738)</p>

      </div>
    </div>
